CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1957, pg. 12 reads: "The Frogs Entertain - The above pictures were taken at the Frogs' first affair during the club's 47th annual celebration of Frogs Week. Held Sunday at the Villa Monaco, members of the club entertained their wives and their out-of-town guests at a swank  cocktail party and buffet supper...Three of the original Frogs at the party are, left to right, Harry G. Washington, Charles Rickmond nad Byron Peters..."
TitMainTitle: FROGS members Harry G. Washington, Charles Rickmond, and Byron Peters, standing in the Villa Monaco for 47th Annual FROGS Week
